<span id="freeTextContainer7471178648344891419">The Physician is the first book of the excellent trilogy (Cole Family) of Noah Gordon I read. A book that I highly recommended if you like such novels &quot;The Pillars of the Earth&quot; in which generations of different eras are mixed, the history of medicine and exciting travel through exotic places.<br/><br/>Spanish version: <br/>El Médico es el primer libro de la excelente trilogía del escritor Noah Gordon. Un libro muy recomendable si te gustan las novelas tipo &quot;Los Pilares de la Tierra&quot; en el que se mezclan gener</span>
  <span id="freeText7471178648344891419" style="display:none">The Physician is the first book of the excellent trilogy (Cole Family) of Noah Gordon I read. A book that I highly recommended if you like such novels "The Pillars of the Earth" in which generations of different eras are mixed, the history of medicine and exciting travel through exotic places.<br /><br />Spanish version: <br />El Médico es el primer libro de la excelente trilogía del escritor Noah Gordon. Un libro muy recomendable si te gustan las novelas tipo "Los Pilares de la Tierra" en el que se mezclan generaciones de épocas diferentes, la historia de la medicina y viajes apasionantes a través de lugares exóticos.<br /></span>
